          "settings": {
            "title": "What makes Uvora different from other milk thistle supplements?",
            "description": "<p>Our milk thistle is standardised to 80% silymarin, the clinical threshold. We use 8 active ingredients that protect and detox simultaneously. And we source naturally under the strictest regulations on the planet.</p>"
